---
source: src/cli/app.rs
expression: "command_help_for_test(\"doctor\")"
---
Check setup, auth, paths, and safety-relevant defaults

Usage: doctor [OPTIONS]

Options:
      --mode <MODE>
          Safety mode to inspect (default: balanced): plan, ask, edit, or auto
          
          [default: default]

      --install-missing
          Install missing opencode/tokei/ctags with mise when mise is available

  -h, --help
          Print help
